    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered. If you're looking for perfection, this is it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
