      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that 'new car' feel inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just a super smooth ride that\u2019s ready for its next home. If you're looking for a ride that's been absolutely pampered, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin. I'd love to show it to you! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 44500.0,
