      "description": "This is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Meticulously preserved, this specimen has had all critical preventative maintenance performed, including rod bearing replacement, a Beisan VANOS overhaul, and professional rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the M-variable limited-slip differential ensures optimal power distribution. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero paint correction needed, while the interior Nappa leather is free of typical bolster wear. A pristine, turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
